<div class="content-wrapper">
  <div class="welcome-message">
    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Welcome back, <strong><%= session.username %></strong>! 👋</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #003D7A;">Ready to connect and grow your professional network?</p>
  </div>

  <% if (session.userType === 'student') { %>
    <h3>📚 Student Dashboard</h3>
    
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🔍</div>
          <h4>Discover Alumni</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Find experienced alumni mentors from your industry and connect with them to gain valuable insights.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/alumni/browse" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Browse Alumni</a>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/alumni/search" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Advanced Search</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🤝</div>
          <h4>My Connections</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Manage and grow your professional network with accepted connections and pending requests.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/connections/my" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">View Connections</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🎤</div>
          <h4>Mock Interviews</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Practice with experienced professionals and prepare for your dream job interviews.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/interviews/my" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">My Interviews</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">👤</div>
          <h4>My Profile</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Keep your profile complete and up-to-date so alumni can find you more easily.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/users/profile" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Edit Profile</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% } else { %>
    <h3>🏢 Alumni Dashboard</h3>
    
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">📬</div>
          <h4>Connection Requests</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Review incoming connection requests from students eager to learn from your experience.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/connections/my" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">View Requests</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🎤</div>
          <h4>My Interviews</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Manage your scheduled and completed mock interview sessions with students.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/interviews/my" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">My Interviews</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">👤</div>
          <h4>My Profile</h4>
        </div>
        <p>Update your professional profile to help students find you and learn about your expertise.</p>
        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/users/profile" class="btn" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Edit Profile</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% } %>
</div>
